  <div class="pb-12 mt-5">
    <div class="text-xl py-1">Hey there ðŸ‘‹</div>
    <div class="text-5xl font-bold">I'm Subinay Panda</div>
    <div class="text-3xl py-3 font-bold">Fullstack Developer and AI-ML Enthusiast</div>
    <div class="py-2">
      <text class="text-lg">
        Passionate developer and AI enthusiast, building innovative solutions in fintech, optimization, and AI-powered SaaS. Always exploring new technologies to solve real-world problems. ðŸš€
      </text>
    </div>
    <div class="mt-8">
      <a class="btn" href="https://linkedin.com/in/subinay-panda" target="_blank"> Let's connect!</a>
      <a href="/Subinay Panda Resume.pdf" target="_blank" class="btn btn-outline ml-5">
        Download Resume
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div>
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold mb-2">My last projects {"</>"}</div>
  </div>

  <HorizontalCard
    title="Sudoku Solver"
    img="/projects/sudoku-solver.webp"
    desc="The Sudoku Solver is an interactive web application designed to assist users in solving Sudoku puzzles with ease. It offers a user-friendly interface where you can input your puzzle directly or upload an image of it. The app provides features like erasing entries, resetting the grid, and solving the puzzle instantly. Built with a responsive design, it ensures compatibility across various devices. This tool is ideal for Sudoku enthusiasts seeking quick solutions or assistance with challenging puzzles."
    url="https://subinay108.github.io/SudokuSolver/"
  />
  <div class="divider my-0"></div>
  <HorizontalCard
    title="Sorting Algorithm Visualizer"
    img="/projects/sorting-algorithm-visualizer.webp"
    desc="Sorting Algorithm Visualizer is a web application that allows users to interactively explore and understand various sorting algorithms. Developed using HTML, CSS, and vanilla JavaScript, this project provides a visually intuitive way to witness how algorithms like Bubble Sort, Quick Sort, Merge Sort, and more, work in real-time."
